Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, when I turned 17...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I was alone with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even now, that scene is burned into my mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The blooming fireworks in the midsummer sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? Saying a thing like that out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That stupid, blank looking face of yours...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can be a pain sometimes, but I think you're a nice girl too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. That's not what I meant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to be embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the new semester starts, we All Hanshin-Kyojin need to do our best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about the two of us auditioning for a comedy show?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:16.48,Sign,,0,0,0,,17th Maido Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:15.72,Superscript,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget what happened that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:16.48,Title,,0,0,0,,Sunk! The Worst Confession in History!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll curse you until your great-grandchildren are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:33.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,Haunted House\N2nd Year Class 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this, you midget...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it so you never laugh again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what the heck is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been cursing me every day since the new semester started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.31,Sign,,0,0,0,,CURSE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to curse you and make you shrink 1cm every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In 156 days, you'll vanish completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You in the ghost costume, and Mr Promoter over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your jobs properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This idiot is spouting pointless crap and getting in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"Idiot"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,An idiot like you shouldn't be calling me an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is wrong with you? You've been upset since back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you really don't know what you did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I gave you my most treasured belonging!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should show me more gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. That, I am thankful for that. I was so happy I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it! I meant after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,After?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.14,0:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Those fireworks sure were pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and find some customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is she so angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's to be expected. Right, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cruel guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! I haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Try searching your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you haven't done anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have something very fun here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... like you, Otani.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That one little phrase...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you know how much effort that took?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.83,Sign,,0,0,0,,2nd Year Class 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Noo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,Haunted House
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,Reception
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan is playing ghost, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.61,0:06:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Su... Su... Su... Suzuku-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,2nd Year Class 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All right everyone, please line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Class Three's haunted house is seriously freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard their ghost will chase you to the ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The school festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,None of that matters to me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's autumn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, we made a ton this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I did work hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're switching shifts in the afternoon. Want to go look around with Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me and Otani?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, you failed once and you're already giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you  mean "failed"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't fail! My confession was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If only his idiocy could be cured...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I seriously thought about whether I'd be able to do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but alas, Otani is too dense for me to get through to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,At this stage it's beyond simple density.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"How about the two of us auditioning for a comedy show?" indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it yourself, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. I don't care about that guy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess. But the class trip is coming up pretty soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do during our free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna hang around with you, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to be alone with my darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's a class trip, for my darling and I, it'll be our first trip away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The romantic night view of Hakodate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...or the canal at Otaru. There's so much I want to experience with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun will want to be alone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So basically you'll be left alone with Otani-kun anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll just be all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san, everyone's looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to come if you're not playing the ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll do the afternoon shift too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.79,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...I know why you're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I did something terrible to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy you like found out that you were with me on your birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...and got the wrong idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh- What's with this cold atmosphere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed he came up with such a complicated theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so surprised I can't even be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not it? That was wrong too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been saying things like that for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is it, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it go again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I like found out and got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so damn annoying. I know that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that's annoyed, you imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"Imbecile"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've heard anyone use that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've had to use it on anyone too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:06.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,ALL HANSHIN KYOJIN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't use weird words like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! You just don't understand because you're so dense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,V + V = 2V
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you make of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't make bad impulse jokes, idiot! Twit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time I've heard that one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem to be well matched, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to step in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The one Risa likes is you, Otani-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are just keeping me in the dark in order to make a fool out of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone bring me something to hit him with!\NSomething that'll really hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought you were lying. What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone lie about something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Haruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, you didn't come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well... the haunted house was a huge hit so she's pretty worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Good timing then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a little rest at our cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's do that, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I made these cookies too. Would you like to try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would, I would!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So your class is running this cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.59,0:11:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. My club is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Home Ec. Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I made club president last time, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Did you say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.10,Sign,,0,0,0,,The Efficiency of Full Dentures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The efficiency of full dentures"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really don't care about me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say "full dentures"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your head is just filled with thoughts of that midget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking about that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.02,0:12:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. You're not thinking about me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know who I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you ask me that?! It's that midget, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,President, I brought some customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.48,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in the Home Ec. Club too, Seiko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a junior member who joined recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what's going on here? Is a volcano erupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chan, this is your fault! Why did you bring that midget here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you have that kind of attitude with a customer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret to inform you that our establishment does not serve gentlemen of diminutive stature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else, Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hey, do you know who Koizumi likes too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I know! Why the hell are you asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I have to verbalize it again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why? What's with this?! What's with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:13:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani's not dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just never thought that I could like him in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, he's never even considered that as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He thinks it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely calm because he thinks it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn midget...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Risa, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Shorty! Stupid midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Just stop, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't like to see you like this, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I found Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch her! Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me your happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is booming. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I think about how Risa is feeling, I just can't feel happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure worked hard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Risa, let's go! It's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the outdoor folk dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an extra girl last year, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm so tall, I ended up in the boys line and had to dance with all the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done with the cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where's Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be alone with my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a huge girl falling for such a short guy, of all people....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani only think of me as his All Kyojin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be laughable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I... like you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? And with all the lights off too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I confessed to the guy I like, but he brushed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... that's no good... I mean... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't I go and try to tell him for you one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:18:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I described the guy I like to you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's shorter than you, he's in the basketball club, he's an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And... he's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Think that"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I don't get you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired of looking at that stupid face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make that face in front of me again, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What- What are you doing! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such an idiot! I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Try getting a clue, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.83,0:20:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shorter than Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In the basketball club...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An idiot like you shouldn't be calling me an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I confessed to the guy I like, but he brushed me off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... like you, Otani.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're embarrassing me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.62,0:20:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She was brushed off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one Risa likes is you, Otani-kun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you ever even think that the guy might be you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M...Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He... He must have realized by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... even if it's just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want him to think of me as a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really the one Koizumi likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bring that up again on the morning of the class trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you're like that that I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:35.63,Sign,,0,0,0,,Bear Curry
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Comeback Impossible! Major Heartbreak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
